                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821016-46-victim533 t17821016-46-viclabel240"></join>, I was coming from my place, No. 133, Upper Thames-street; and this box was lost out of the coach on the 5th of October; there were two or three boxes put in, and one was taken out; the box I lost was opened at the Mansion House.</p>
