                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821016-46-off238 t17821016-46-crimeloc241"></join>, and I saw the prisoner put his hand into the coach, take out a box, and call to a man by the name of Will to come and take it, I said Will shall not take it, and the prosecutrix came and claimed it: the prisoner said, if he ever got clear he would do me for it.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I know nothing of it.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called one witness who gave him a good character.</p>
